rComments: Great class for beginners. The majority of each class was spent weight lifting, but there was always time left for a brief cardio workout. Danielle was a knowledgeable and friendly trainer.

Danielle is great, very nice and friendly. She makes working out fun and different everytime. She has an endless library of knowledge and type of workouts. Accomodating to all workout levels. I enjoyed the class very much, it gave me new and improved perspective of weight training after years of it since high school.
